title: In 2026, AI will outwrite humans
description: In 2026, AI-written content will outpace what humans produce — not just in spammy corners of the web, but across the mainstream channels where people search, scroll, and learn. This isn’t a story about technological capability. We already know machines can generate limitless words. It’s a story about volume, value, and what journalism becomes when...
